pullRequest.body:
Given a `G`-representation `A` and a normal subgroup `S` of `G`, this PR defines the corestriction-coinflation short complex 
`H‚ÇÅ(S, A) ‚ü∂ H‚ÇÅ(G, A) ‚ü∂ H‚ÇÅ(G ‚ß∏ S, A_S)` induced by the natural inclusion `S ‚Üí G` and projections `G ‚Üí G / S, A ‚Üí A_S`. We proves it's exact, and that the righthand map is an epimorphism.

---
